cleaned_text: Naturopathic Phone Consultation Naturopathic Phone Consultation $360.50 Purchase this consultation and you will receive the following: - This is a 60 minute scheduled phone consultation - Symptom Based Questionnaire will be emailed to you prior to scheduled appointment - Food chart will be emailed to you - Included with this consultation are suggestions for supplements/Energy Patches based upon your symptom questionnaire answers as well as review of the food chart and nutritional guidance This is the initial naturopathic phone consultation. If you have already completed this, [find the follow-up here](https://www.atlantapsychotherapyandenergymedicine.com/purchase-a-session/p4nmp4vusylfipdrg44s3ed5qv25u1) * Alison does not advocate that any of the information on this site be taken as medical guidance or advice. The dietary and supplemental suggestions are not prescribed or in lieu of any medications you are currently taking. Quantity: Add To Cart This is a 60 minute scheduled phone consultation, with Alison, that includes the following: - Review of a symptom based questionnaire that will be emailed to you prior to the scheduled consultation date - Review of suggested supplements and/or Energy Patches that support your goals and related to questionnaire answers - Review of food choice options, including an e-mailed Food Chart guide
